的一切<br />\n<br />\n但如果你乜撚都無睇過，只不過得閒會諗人生有乜意義咁上下，或者睇過一本哲學入門覺得幾得意咁，屌咁都係揀專科啦，你買呢一個degree要成16萬現金架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係一個對人生未來嘅大投資嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700cfa63e4c4ed5cf6ade2d00834733b21d8cfab","tid":2120428,"uid":116390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:03:20.000Z","msg":"其實三大同非三大有個冇乜人留意嘅分別<br />\n係三大係相對容易識到勁人<br />\n呢樣對中下分數特別係冇家底嘅影響好大<br />\n好多時中下層係唔識點玩有用嘅活動同比賽<br />\n到時聽得多勁人講起碼知有咩可以揀"},{"pid":"e91b808a5e1bfc431cbd014a0b8f69e77bdbf514","tid":2120428,"uid":154328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:03:47.000Z","msg":"八大都唔洗爭，學店贏曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n東華PT同OT點睇<br />\n學費sssdp完一年70k，讀4年280k<br />\n大學engine學費一年40k，讀4年160k<br />\n學費差額120k<br />\n而出嚟做野fg價嚟講<br />\n工程當你fg18k 第2年20k 當你有14個月糧<br />\n2年加埋賺532k<br />\n而東華PT同OT fg30k<br />\n當你2年都30k 總共就720k<br />\n差額已經差188k 夠補翻學費差額120k有突多68k<br />\n仲要冇engine咁多ot咁辛苦<br />\n東華PT同OT真係好似好抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fb5e2b1b688c60a6ecfe55444c16b84622378e","tid":2120428,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:22:43.000Z","msg":"飄洋過海到英國G5升學 或成文社科學術科最佳出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2120750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2120750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}